    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "和林格尔县文化旅游体育局[]：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "安徽建工建设投资集团有限公司根据《中华人民共和国文物保护法》《内蒙古自治区文物保护条例》要求，于2026年3月对S27呼和浩特至鄂尔多斯高速公路(呼和浩特段)项目(一标段)沥青拌合站临时用地项目占地范围进行文物勘探工作，项目位于和林格尔县巧什营镇圪报村，勘探面积:51444平方米。在此次文物勘探工作中，无文物遗存发现[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "根据指导意见，现将S27呼和浩特至鄂尔多斯高速公路(呼和浩特段)项目(一标段)沥青拌合站临时用地项目文物勘探报告随文呈报并请贵局予以审批备案[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "此请示，请复。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
